snippet.textDisplay: This song has baazi vibes to it and is such a fun filled siraiki number. Both Sahir and Aima have done complete justice to it. They made it so beautiful that I am sure so many people would have wanted to dance to the addictive tune as I  did. I personally have loved this year's coke studio except one or two songs and I am unable to understand why some people aren't appreciating the experimentation and innovation of this platform in this season instead of demanding a more Bollywood style of music. We should all broaden our horizons musically.
